Taxonomy. 
<taxonomicName authority="Thomas, 1896" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1896" box="[880,1292,2827,2852]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Acomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="4" pageNumber="601" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="louisae">Acomys louisae Thomas, 1896</taxonomicName>
, 40 mi (64-5 km) south of Berbera, Soma-lia.
</paragraph>
