<paragraph blockId="4.[1365,2573,300,644]" box="[1366,1740,458,487]" pageId="4" pageNumber="601">Breeding. No information.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[1365,2573,300,644]" box="[1365,2094,493,527]" pageId="4" pageNumber="601">Activity patterns. Louise’s Spiny Mouse is terrestrial.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[1365,2573,300,644]" box="[1366,2306,532,566]" pageId="4" pageNumber="601">Movements, Home range and Social organization. No information.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
